@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
[*] --> Reviewed
Reviewed --> Cancelled : process
Reviewed : entry / log librarian
Cancelled --> Delivered : approve
Delivered --> Processing : update
Processing --> Approved : cancel
Approved --> Archived : approve
Approved : entry / log librarian
Cancelled --> Delivered : revert
Archived --> [*]
@enduml